en: 1. Accept an offer for a pack token below
zh_CN: 1. 接受下面的包代币报价

en: 2. Send token to the redemption address
zh_CN: 2. 将代币发送至赎回地址

en: 3. Within 5-30 minutes depending on network conditions you will receive the minted cards in your wallet.
zh_CN: 3. 根据网络状况5-30 分钟内您将在钱包中收到铸造的卡。

en: 4. For the cards to show in your account and to be playable they must be transferred to your DID. You can do this in the CHIA GUI with the bulk transfer option.
zh_CN: 4. 为了让卡牌显示在您的帐户中并可以玩，它们必须转移到您的 DID。您可以在 CHIA GUI 中使用批量传输选项来执行此操作。

en: * Cards may be minted across multiple blocks
